reviews.text: I am very impressed with this airport, it is very clean well kept. I wasn't able to make my connection here so they put me up in a hotel for free, it was awesome. Also their airport is beautiful, there are not very many airports that look really good be this one does. Also the atmosphere was great everyone was in a hurry but very polite and respectful.

Good airport, I think this clean and beautiful one is the best airport around the world! Of course the staffs are super kind and good hospitality! Not only the hospitality, they have food restaurants, free tables, good souvenirs shops and small exhibitions. Even though you don’t have a flight you can come and relax with good foods and enjoy airplanes on the roof top observation deck! Open air so you can enjoy taking good photos!! Enjoy!
Nice airport.Very well planned. Very easy to get along there. Everything went fast. It was super comfortable . it was not crowded. I wish there were more airports like this one around the world..

Great airport, large spacious and clean. Was not overly busy, plenty of gift shops for the last minute souvenir hunter. Public transport was easy to use with the monorail running to all three terminals. By far the best airport I have been to.
This airport is very well connected to downtown Japan.  The airport itself is clean, and plenty of restaurants and facilities in the international terminal.  Pleasant airport to fly out of.
